# Quick Reference Guide

## Common Commands
```bash
# Development Setup
bun install                    # Install dependencies
bun run install-hooks         # Install Git hooks

# Development Tasks
bun test                      # Run all tests
bun run typecheck            # Type checking
bun run format               # Format code
bun run format:check         # Check formatting

# Specific Test Files
bun test trigger-validation   # Test trigger logic
bun test create-prompt       # Test prompt generation
bun test image-downloader    # Test image processing
```

